{"id": "1409472482678669432", "channel_id": "1409472482678669432", "type": 0, "author_id": "183623179455954945", "author_name": "luka.s", "author_bot": false, "content": "I’m not sure if this is a bug or intended, but if it’s intended I believe it doesn’t really go with the spirit of the paradox covenant set and should be changed.\n\nThe way the paradox set is supposed to work is that it is supposed to increase the cost of your first exalt without increasing the cost of subsequent exalts. The way this is implemented is by increasing the aliemus cap for exalts to 120, but keeping the amount of aliemus depleted when using exalt at 100, so after you exalt you are supposed to have 20 aliemus still and therefore after the first exalt you’ll always have at most 100 aliemus left to go.\n\nSeems fine, but increasing the cap by 20 also increases the cap by 40 for overexalt, and the cap is now 240. So the consumption for overexalt should also be kept at 200, right, so it still only increases the cost of the first overexalt in practice?\n\nWell, I think that’s how it should work, but right now it doesn’t. Right now paradox set just increases your overexalt cost as well, not just the cap, which means in practice you can’t really overexalt at all on awakeners using the paradox covenant set. See this video: https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1324466524383350874/1409469474750464072/ScreenRecording_08-25-2025_02-26-30_1.mov?ex=68ad7e3d&is=68ac2cbd&hm=6ae90ba632b3eb510e6d96d61660a92a6e6dc7f250a102ee242d9d658876256d&\n\nIf this a bug, it would make OE Kathy feel a bit better if it was fixed, and if it’s an intended feature I believe it should be changed.\n\nThanks!", "timestamp": "2025-08-25T09:40:26.603000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Emoji_LT_R_02", "emoji_id": "1400771683664658433", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "huh1", "emoji_id": "1356053088552747141", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "", "url": "https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1324466524383350874/1409469474750464072/ScreenRecording_08-25-2025_02-26-30_1.mov?ex=68ad7e3d&is=68ac2cbd&hm=6ae90ba632b3eb510e6d96d61660a92a6e6dc7f250a102ee242d9d658876256d&", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409472482678669432", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」“Bug” with paradox and overexalt?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "1361168893200044183"]}
