{"id": "1409521445020635136", "channel_id": "1409521445020635136", "type": 0, "author_id": "116380262845251590", "author_name": "madlax", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello,\n\nSo, i was wondering why those 3 girls didn't join the Realm's banners at the end of their reruns.\nWas it a mistake or will they never become standard?\n\nMaybe is it because of \"Before Memories Fade\" banners that are currently available ? So what about in 52 days when they're done ?\n\nBecause if we don't update the realm's banners, then at some point, Pure core are becoming kind of useless, i have 524 pure core right now, not even 1 year in the game yet, finished my wheels and team, idk what to do with it anymore if we don't add units in those banners.", "timestamp": "2025-08-25T12:55:00.135000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "👎", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1409521445331144875", "filename": "trio.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 550732, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1409521445020635136/1409521445331144875/trio.jpg?ex=69cbc424&is=69ca72a4&hm=1d9d28b5d2900034cc8f84df7f746b4eab79069e51930330e65f8632c7e38e10&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409521445020635136", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」About Myriam/Thais/Wanda", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
